Class CEDD

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.metadatasearch.lire.feature.CEDD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.semanticmetadata.lire.imageanalysis.LireFeature, ImageLireFeature

    public class CEDD
extends Object
implements ImageLireFeature
    The CEDD feature was created, implemented and provided by Savvas A. Chatzichristofis
    More information can be found in: Savvas A. Chatzichristofis and Yiannis S. Boutalis, CEDD: Color and Edge Directivity Descriptor. A Compact Descriptor for Image Indexing and Retrieval, A. Gasteratos, M. Vincze, and J.K. Tsotsos (Eds.): ICVS 2008, LNCS 5008, pp. 312-322, 2008.
